name: VERY STRANGE STORY
description:
I suggest you try a game. You will become the creators of the story we will write together.

There are only 5 tokens for this first episode. Everyone who buys one will answer one of the questions:

1. Who is the main character the story is being told from? And what is his name?
2. Where are the main characters located?
3. What is the name of the girl sleeping in the bed? And who is she?
4. How and where did these two meet, and do they even know each other?
5. What the hell was going on last night?

When all 5 tokens are sold, I'll draw the second episode and we'll continue the game.

I wonder what will happen next...

P.S. Please, once you buy one of the tokens, contact me on Twitter and I'll ask you one of these 5 questions.
